---
import { Image } from 'astro:assets';
import profile from '../assets/profile.jpg'
---

<div class="overflow-hidden bg-white py-24 sm:py-32 dark:bg-gray-900">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-6 lg:px-8">
        <div class="mx-auto grid max-w-2xl grid-cols-1 gap-x-8 gap-y-16 sm:gap-y-20 lg:mx-0 lg:max-w-none lg:grid-cols-2">
            <div class="lg:pt-4 lg:pr-8">
                <div class="lg:max-w-lg">
                    <p class="mt-2 text-4xl font-semibold tracking-tight text-pretty text-gray-900 sm:text-5xl dark:text-white">
                        Planner. Doer. Solver.
                    </p>
                    <p class="mt-6 text-lg/8 text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300">
                        Engineering and economics are the tools I use to solve complex problems.
                        Incrementalism is how I get to the desired outcome.
                        I develop software to improve the human-experience, not to replace it.
                        So much of our world is focused on fear and uncertainty, but my career is dedicated to providing solutions and optimism.
                    </p>
                    <p class="mt-6 text-lg/8 text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300">
                        A software engineer by trade with over 13 years of experience building scalable B2B enterprise solutions
                        across the full technology stack. Able to launch brand new products or dive deep into legacy codebases.
                        Practical technical expertise spanning design, web development, data engineering, DevOps, and security.
                        Product focused and agility minded, I've guide development teams through complex technical projects
                        while keeping alignment with customer needs and business objectives at the forefront.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <Image src={profile} layout="constrained" alt="Mag Jiraboondilok" class="w-3xl max-w-none rounded-xl shadow-xl ring-1 ring-gray-400/10 not-dark:hidden sm:w-228 md:-ml-4 lg:-ml-0 dark:ring-white/10" />
            <Image src={profile} alt="Mag Jiraboondilok" class="w-3xl max-w-none rounded-xl shadow-xl ring-1 ring-gray-400/10 sm:w-228 md:-ml-4 lg:-ml-0 dark:hidden dark:ring-white/10" />
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
